lead_paragraph: Promoted RB Leipzig always expected their first Bundesliga season to be a turbulent affair but they seem to have gotten more than they bargained for with their sensational start that has seen them go top of the table after 10 matches.

headline.print_headline: Promoted Leipzig Brush Off Critics to Go Top of the Table
